## Deployment
+ Apply a EC2 service on AWS, create ssl certificate
+ Install secureCRT to login Amazon cloud server, install tomcat and mysql on it
+ Pack the project: npm run build, generate the deployment file under the directory: docs/demos/temp
+ Copy all the file under docs/demos/temp directory to the /usr/share/tomcat/webapps/Hotmel/tomcat and the website will be deployed automatically

## Backend environment
+ Install developmeny IDE: IntelliJ
+ Install maven 3.6.0

+ Configure pom.xml to install the dependencies automatically
+ Configure the port number in the application.yml
+ Set packing to jar in pom.xml to pack into jar package
+ Put the package onto the Amazon cloud server: nohup java -jar packageName.jar
